Packages
com.orindasoft.pub Provides classes and interfaces used by JDBCWizard 6.0.3145 generated code.

 

Using the com.orindasoft.pub Java Class Libraries

This information is taken from the JDBCWizard Manual

If you are looking for general information on how to use JDBCWizard you should try the JDBCWizard Documentation Webpage 

Rather than using these libraries directly you should use the JDBCWizard GUI to generate code that uses them.

Generated code uses the com.orindasoft.pub class libraries for logging and managing retrieved data. There is a class library version for each Oracle release supported by OrindaBuild. The libraries are located in the following directories:

Location... Library... Description...
InstallDir/lib/815 OrindaBuildPub815.jar Compiled Java Class Library for use with Oracle 8.1.5
InstallDir/lib/816 OrindaBuildPub816.jar Compiled Java Class Library for use with Oracle 8.1.6
InstallDir/lib/817 OrindaBuildPub817.jar Compiled Java Class Library for use with Oracle 8.1.7
InstallDir/lib/901 OrindaBuildPub901.jar Compiled Java Class Library for use with Oracle 9.0.1
InstallDir/lib/920 OrindaBuildPub920.jar Compiled Java Class Library for use with Oracle 9.2.0
InstallDir/lib/1010 OrindaBuildPub1010.jar
 Compiled Java Class Library for use with Oracle 10.1.0


If you license a full version of OrindaBuild the library source code is located in the following directories:

Location... Zip File... Description...
InstallDir/src OrindaBuildPubApi815.zip Java Source Library for use with Oracle 8.1.5
InstallDir/src OrindaBuildPubApi816.zip Java Source Library for use with Oracle 8.1.6
InstallDir/src OrindaBuildPubApi817.zip Java Source Library for use with Oracle 8.1.7
InstallDir/src OrindaBuildPubApi901.zip Java Source Library for use with Oracle 9.0.1
InstallDir/src OrindaBuildPubApi920.zip Java Source Library for use with Oracle 9.2.0
InstallDir/src OrindaBuildPubApi1010.zip Java Source Library for use with Oracle 10.1.0

Note: Orinda Software can not guarantee that future releases and builds of OrindaBuild will not make changes to the com.orindasoft.pub java class libraries. We will attempt to avoid changes which would break existing applications.
